The '''Steward of the Imperial Personal Archives''' was the being who controlled all access to and input in the [[Imperial Personal Archives]]. At the time of the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]] the position was held by [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]], who used it to seal all records on [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] [[House Palpatine/Legends|family]] and personal relationships.

